### List available pets - public
GET {{baseUrl}}/pets/available

### Create user - public
# @name createUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Usuario Teste",
    "email": "usuario.teste.{{$timestamp}}@email.com",
